'''机智号'''（{{lang-en|'''Ingenuity'''}}，也称“'''小机灵'''”({{lang|en|'''Ginny'''}})<ref>{{Cite web|title=NASA“毅力”号核动力火星车发射成功，还携带了一架直升机！_科技_腾讯网|url=https://tech.qq.com/a/20200730/017912.htm|accessdate=2020-08-11|work=tech.qq.com|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421142155/https://tech.qq.com/a/20200730/017912.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=NASA“毅力”号核动力火星车发射升空，还带了一架直升机|url=https://tech.sina.cn/2020-07-30/detail-iivhuipn5955450.d.html|accessdate=2020-08-11|date=2020-07-30|last=sina_mobile|work=tech.sina.cn|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307200020/https://tech.sina.cn/2020-07-30/detail-iivhuipn5955450.d.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是一台[[火星|火星]]无人直升机<ref name="NASA-20200429a">{{cite news|last1=Hautaluoma|first1=Grey|last2=Johnson|first2=Alana|last3=Agle|first3=D.C.|title=Alabama High School Student Names NASA's Mars Helicopter|url=https://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?feature=7650|date=2020-04-29|work=NASA|access-date=2020-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200430003052/https://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?feature=7650|archive-date=2020-04-30|url-status=|author=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=}} {{PD-notice}}</ref><ref name="distance">[https://www.uasvision.com/2016/09/06/nasa-chooses-helicopter-for-mars-drone/ Mars Helicopter Scout] {{Wayback|url=https://www.uasvision.com/2016/09/06/nasa-chooses-helicopter-for-mars-drone/ |date=20190817152011 }}. video presentation at Caltech {{PD-notice}}</ref>，是第一架“在另一个星球上进行动力控制飞行”的飞行器<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":3">{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-56799755|title=NASA successfully flies small helicopter on Mars|publisher=BBC|date=2021-04-19|accessdate=2021-04-19|archive-date=2021-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210529144921/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-56799755|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[火星2020|火星2020]]任务中用来进行飞行技术验证，它可以提供目前轨道卫星或地面探测车和着陆器无法提供的独特视角。为探测器或人类提供高清晰度图像和侦察，并使探测车能够进入难以到达的地形<ref name="Leone heli">{{cite news|last=Leone|first=Dan|url=http://spacenews.com/elachi-touts-helicopter-scout-for-mars-sample-caching-rover/|title=Elachi Touts Helicopter Scout for Mars Sample-Caching Rover|work=|date=2015-11-19|access-date=2015-11-20|author=|publisher=|accessdate=|language=|format=|archive-date=2016-01-21|archive-url=https://archive.today/20160121214139/http://spacenews.com/elachi-touts-helicopter-scout-for-mars-sample-caching-rover/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

机智号在着陆后约60天从[[毅力号|毅力号]]腹下分离，并于2021年4月3日部署。<ref name="NASA-20200623">{{cite news|last1=Agle|first1=DC|last2=Hautaluoma|first2=Gray|last3=Johnson|first3=Alana|title=How NASA's Mars Helicopter Will Reach the Red Planet's Surface|url=https://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/nws.php?feature=7684|date=2020-06-23|publisher=[[NASA|NASA]]|access-date=2020-06-23|archive-date=2021-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221200008/https://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/nws.php?feature=7684|dead-url=no}} {{PD-notice}}</ref><ref name="Today">{{cite news | title = Mars Rover Perseverance Set To Launch Drone | newspaper = Today | publisher = [[YouTube|YouTube]] | date = 2021-03-24 | url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2ceFiynmNB0&ab_channel=TODAY | access-date = 2021-03-27 | archive-date = 2021-04-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210415113502/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2ceFiynmNB0&ab_channel=TODAY | dead-url = no }}</ref> 与毅力号分离后将开展为期30天的飞行测试，飞行高度距地面3至5米，飞行距离可达300米（980英尺），每次飞行不超过三分钟，最多飞行五次。<ref>[https://rotorcraft.arc.nasa.gov/Publications/files/Balaram_AIAA2018_0023.pdf Mars Helicopter Technology Demonstrator] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401121747/https://rotorcraft.arc.nasa.gov/Publications/files/Balaram_AIAA2018_0023.pdf|date=2019-04-01|title=}}. (PDF) J. (Bob) Balaram, Timothy Canham, Courtney Duncan, Matt Golombek, Håvard Fjær Grip, Wayne Johnson, Justin Maki, Amelia Quon, Ryan Stern, and David Zhu. American Institute of Aeronautics and Astronautics (AIAA), SciTech Forum Conference; January 8–12, 2018, Kissimmee, Florida. {{doi|10.2514/6.2018-0023}} {{PD-notice}}</ref>机智号可以在飞行中进行自主控制，每次降落后，它将直接与毅力号通信。<ref>{{Cite web|title=First Flight on Another Planet! - YouTube|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GhsZUZmJvaM|accessdate=2020-08-05|work=www.youtube.com|archive-date=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728075025/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GhsZUZmJvaM|dead-url=no}}</ref> 机智号的首次试飞时间定在2021年4月19日上午3:15 [[北美东部时区|EDT]]（7:15 [[协调世界时|UTC]]），[[網路直播|網路直播]]則在三小時之後的6:15 EDT（10:15 UTC）進行。<ref name="MH-status-290">{{cite web|title=Work Progresses Toward Ingenuity's First Flight on Mars|url=https://mars.nasa.gov/technology/helicopter/status/290/work-progresses-toward-ingenuity-s-first-flight-on-mars/|website=NASA Mars Helicopter Tech Demo|publisher=NASA|date=2021-04-12|access-date=2021-04-18|archive-date=2021-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419100613/https://mars.nasa.gov/technology/helicopter/status/290/work-progresses-toward-ingenuity-s-first-flight-on-mars/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ingenuity passes full speed test">{{cite web|date=2021-04-17|title=Mars Helicopter completed full-speed spin test|url=https://twitter.com/NASA/status/1383221042504638464|access-date=2021-04-17|website=Twitter|publisher=NASA|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417114123/https://twitter.com/NASA/status/1383221042504638464|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Tech_Demo">{{cite web|title = Mars Helicopter Tech Demo|work = Watch Online|publisher = [[NASA|NASA]]|date = 2021-04-18|url = https://mars.nasa.gov/technology/helicopter/#Watch-Online|accessdate = 2021-04-18|archive-date = 2020-04-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200416082901/https://mars.nasa.gov/technology/helicopter/#Watch-Online|dead-url = no}}</ref> 机智号的首飞试验获得成功，这是人类首次实现飞行器在其他星球的受控飞行<ref name=":3" />。

机智号将在30个火星日（约31个地球日）的窗口期内执行后续4次试飞任务。任务团队将通过獨創号验证在火星大气层飞行所需要的技术，为筹备未来机器人或人类探索火星时携带的先进飞行器打下基础。这些直升机将能在未来的探测任务中担任辅助角色，例如：作为机器人侦察员，从上方勘测地形或作为独立科学飞行器来携带仪器。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=NASA“毅力”号发射升空！_《环球科学》（“科学美国人”中文版）【唯一官方网站】|url=https://huanqiukexue.com/a/qianyan/tianwen__wuli/2020/0731/30178.html|accessdate=2020-08-06|work=huanqiukexue.com|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204082531/https://huanqiukexue.com/a/qianyan/tianwen__wuli/2020/0731/30178.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=科普：美国“毅力”号火星车有何独特之处-新华网|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2020-07/31/c_1126306699.htm|accessdate=2020-08-06|work=www.xinhuanet.com|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307200057/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2020-07/31/c_1126306699.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>   至 2022年4月 29日已執行 28次任務，然而原訂 5月3日展開的第 29 次飛行，機智號首次與 NASA 失去聯繫。目前已恢復通訊並確認異常原因隨著火星冬季即將到來前景開始變得險峻。

